---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DonateCTA from '@/components/DonateCTA.astro';
import { SITE } from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout title="Support" description="Support Shelf Check and keep food recall coverage public.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-amber">Support Shelf Check</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-headline text-5xl uppercase text-navy">Independent coverage tastes better.</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-700">If Shelf Check saves you time, stories, or a suspect snack, support the project so the data pipeline and editorial work stay public.</p>
    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_380px]">
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p>Support helps cover build minutes, image generation, data refreshes, and the occasional raccoon-grade burst of indignation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Daily and weekly FDA collection workflows</li>
          <li>Open-source static hosting on GitHub Pages</li>
          <li>Git-based editorial workflow through Keystatic</li>
          <li>Shareable graphics and accountability snapshots</li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href={SITE.donateUrl}>Back the project on GitHub Sponsors</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <DonateCTA />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
